---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Banner from '../components/Banner.astro';
import CTA from '../components/CTA.astro';
import SubjectsGrid from '../components/SubjectsGrid.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us" description="Learn about Boldtutor's private tutoring services for high school and university students in Sydney.">
  <Header slot="header" />

  <Banner title="About Us" />

  <section class="py-section">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6">
      <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none prose-headings:font-heading prose-headings:uppercase prose-a:text-primary-light hover:prose-a:text-primary">
        <h2>Why Boldtutor</h2>

        <p>Firstly, high school work and the year 12 HSC course may result in <a href="https://lighthouse.mq.edu.au/article/october2/Doing-the-HSC-does-not-cause-undue-stress,-new-research#:~:text=HSC%20stress%20aligns%20with%20the%20national%20average&text=%E2%80%9CWe%20found%20that%20HSC%20students,12%2C%20but%20not%20critically.%E2%80%9D">increased stress levels</a> for high school students according to a 2019 study from Macquarie University.</p>

        <p>Secondly, HSC students have similar or slightly higher distress than the national average at the start of Year 12, and this stress may increase over the course of HSC study.</p>

        <p>With this in mind, an effective approach to deal with this stress is to consider hiring me as your high school tutor or HSC tutor from Boldtutor. This is because I offer exclusive resources and dedicated guidance to help you understand how to write an essay among other tasks.</p>

        <p>Furthermore, I provide private tutor sessions starting from 1 hour. This is great because my Sydney tutoring service will provide chances for you to revise your work during the session and after the session has been completed.</p>

        <p>Booking with Boldtutor also helps me support a great cause – <a href="https://www.four-paws.org.au/">Four Paws Animal Welfare charity</a>.</p>

        <p>Additionally, feel free to check out my <a href="http://www.boldtutor.com.au/">samples of success</a> gallery on Boldtutor's homepage to see the strong results achieved by some of my clients.</p>

        <h2>My Private Tutor Services</h2>

        <h6>FIND OUT WHAT I CAN DO FOR YOU</h6>

        <p>Firstly, Boldtutor provides the following services for high school clients:</p>

        <ul>
          <li>Private tutor starting from 1 hour sessions</li>
          <li>Sydney tutoring at your desired location</li>
          <li>Assignment help/feedback</li>
          <li>Exclusive notes</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Subjects Taught</h2>

        <h6>BY ALL MEANS, FOR WHATEVER TOPIC, TEXT OR ASSIGNMENT, BOLDTUTOR HAS YOU COVERED. THIS IS BECAUSE I, YOUR PRIVATE TUTOR, HAVE STUDIED ALL THE TOPICS BELOW:</h6>

        <SubjectsGrid subjects={[
          { title: 'English', description: 'Henry IV · The Tempest · The Crucible · Hag-Seed · Billy Elliot · Craft of Writing · 1984 · And more…', href: 'http://boldtutor.com.au/english-services/', icon: 'book' },
          { title: 'University', description: 'Philosophy · Politics · Humanities · Media · Cultural Studies · Journalism · History · Teaching (Secondary)', href: 'http://boldtutor.com.au/university-tuition/', icon: 'graduation' },
          { title: 'Modern History', description: 'History yr 7-11 · Peace and Conflict · Power & Authority in Modern World · National Studies · Change in the Modern World', href: 'http://boldtutor.com.au/subjects/modern-history/', icon: 'history' },
          { title: 'Society and Culture', description: 'PIP · Social Theory · Research Methodologies · Depth Studies', href: 'http://boldtutor.com.au/subjects/society-and-culture/', icon: 'society' },
        ]} />

        <h2>Why University Tuition with Boldtutor</h2>

        <p>Altogether, studies show that university leads <a href="https://headspace.org.au/blog/majority-of-aussie-students-stressed-depressed/">to severe stress for 70 percent of students.</a>. This is because students have to balance university exams and university study with other priorities such as work etc. Overall, this can lead to poor performance.</p>

        <p>However, with Boldtutor's university tuition, I offer as your private tutor the exclusive notes and guidance you need to ace university courses specialising in Bachelor of Arts, Bachelor of Education and other specialities. In addition, I offer:</p>

        <ul>
          <li><a href="http://boldtutor.com.au/money-back-guarantee-university-tuition-assignment-help/">Money back guarantee</a> for assignment help</li>
          <li>Private tutor/detailed sessions starting from 90 minutes</li>
          <li>Sydney tutoring at your desired location</li>
          <li>Assignment help/feedback during and after completion of session</li>
          <li>Exclusive notes that will accordingly improve understanding of course</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Furthermore, scroll down to my <a href="http://www.boldtutor.com.au/">samples of success</a> gallery on the homepage and don't forget to ask for my assignment help guarantee for clients that have booked an assignment session with Boldtutor.</p>

        <p><a href="http://boldtutor.com.au/">Book me as your private tutor today</a>.</p>
      </article>

    </div>
  </section>

  <CTA />

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</BaseLayout>
